          <a href="https://www.cvs.com/" target="_blank">
          <img src="images/cvslogo.png" alt="CVS logo"> </a>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-box8">
          <h6>Mission Statement</h6>
          <p> CVS Health is dedicated to improving the lives of our customers by providing accessible, high-quality healthcare and pharmacy services. We aim to be a trusted partner for our communities, offering a wide range of products and services to meet their needs.  </p>
